{"tid":1998344,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"(未fc) 家長: 不滿被屈毛, 以後唔再出錢俾手足","createTime":"2020-05-02T10:27:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-03T04:12:52.000Z","uid":134071,"like":4,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"090bc94bce813fcd8ebc194aeffd6db3d8d76f3f","tid":1998344,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T10:27:08.000Z","msg":"有家長跟癲狗記者駁火, 之後有人唱衰家長<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1997601/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1997601/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n而家, 高登有人自稱受捐者, 話相關家長不滿自己被屈毛, 決定以後唔撚再出錢俾手足<br />\n<img src=\"http://na.cx/i/f9zovAU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ff9zovAU.jpg&h=0d5cb7d7&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其實黃圈真係需要有糾紛調解機制.<br />\n但唔好立亂係連登將不和公開, 更唔好立亂屈毛.<br />\n<br />\n而家, 手足輸(少左家長), 泛民輸 (d高登仔當係泛民迫走家長)<br />\n只有老左土共贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n記住, <strong>be humble, 不分化</strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5396469b64d4a8b0119e8ea48d77a5d22432412b","tid":1998344,"uid":134071,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T10:27:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過我都唔明點解高登仔可以入飯民數?<br />\n<br />\n家長係屌癲狗記者, <br />\n癲狗唔係飯民, 咁飯民有咩必要屌家長?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5337bcc86273c88dfc5aa9cfaca04a0c12976c07","tid":1998344,"uid":41861,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T10:28:11.000Z","msg":"高登<br />\n完"},{"pid":"13d206453eb7dfbce15513f64651456cde478c2b","tid":1998344,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T10:28:20.000Z","msg":"不分化, 以和為貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d75aae51f83cbe2c4e6a63ba14aa450238f677b9","tid":1998344,"uid":112622,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime"